{"tid":857282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【施政報告】評分大跌　林鄭：預期之內　認不少措施有爭議","createTime":"2018-10-11T03:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T04:36:08.000Z","uid":192190,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e35186061cb0cd3be00295bffee452083bcfb1cf","tid":857282,"uid":192190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T03:59:31.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥昨日發表任內第二份《施政報告》，惟市民對報告評分較去年大跌，以100分滿分計平均只有48.5分，較去年少近14分。林鄭月娥今早於電台聯播節目中稱「這反應是預期之內」，因《施政報告》有很多措施，當中不少是有爭議措施，「有一項措施得罪百分之十的人，就會引來不滿」，如禁電子煙、填海及取消強積金對沖等，又透露「一向緊密伙伴都有些意見」。<br />\n林鄭月娥又說，處理較重大議題時需要很長遠規劃，「如果第二份（任內第二份《施政報告》）都不提出，就沒什麼機會提到」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭: 吹咩吹咩? 咬我食呀? 哈哈哈哈!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2e77365f7ff4defbb6c2a49094a337c547a957","tid":857282,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T04:12:28.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f18f226a2dd4a70f46cf3767b1bbb5100bba36","tid":857282,"uid":178205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T04:14:19.000Z","msg":"大雄:我考試低分係預期之內，唔使改，只係同老師對答案嘅睇法有分歧<br />\n<br />\n大雄媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249b08ec674ed5b315de43e8256ce7af3ffdcb43","tid":857282,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T04:36:08.000Z","msg":"走撚開柒波"}]}